snippet.title: Time Wasters Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Time Wasters is a space shooter roguelite. Equip and upgrade weapons, destroy swarms of enemies, and collect Time Cubes to bend the timeline to your advantage.

Time Wasters on Steam Early Access:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1290330/Time_Wasters/
